{"tid":828560,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"每晚返屋企仲有冇開電腦?","createTime":"2018-09-19T19:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T13:17:33.000Z","uid":123991,"like":15,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8f648ce09e7ae4351dcba035a05bd77714254c6a","tid":828560,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:00:44.000Z","msg":"有時聽人講話屋企部電腦都唔知幾耐冇開覺得好恐怖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話咩篤下電話篤下平板就得,  完全想像唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常電腦都有個 20&quot; 以上嘅 mon 睇野唔洗左掃右掃<br />\n又有 keyboard 打字又快, load 網頁速度更加唔洗講<br />\nchrome extension 果類更加唔洗比<br />\n究竟話冇開電腦呢句說話有幾可信? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時比人問到我有冇開電腦我都會答冇, 但實情晚晚都開緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 都用緊網頁版連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4e2c2e8f26e675c4a8b42f191f4e958a249c6a","tid":828560,"uid":199291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:01:38.000Z","msg":"好耐冇開"},{"pid":"e41543368a2aa0921588f34571c5128e1af455ab","tid":828560,"uid":31173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"打J先開下"},{"pid":"e64eb6bce88ea323cbecfdc5e969a46dc8ff7dad","tid":828560,"uid":76347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:26:06.000Z","msg":"電視當mon <br />\n想睇野一定開電腦"},{"pid":"b10bf6fd4adae6c2bf58e072efc39a384950fb3f","tid":828560,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:39:54.000Z","msg":"我好多fd屋企連電腦都無又點睇<br />\n話用平板夠哂皮"},{"pid":"b7061b8eed518ee4a167a187495abb6cec5ab672","tid":828560,"uid":43850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:47:47.000Z","msg":"有好多野都係電話ipad取代唔到<br />\n例如打機 做野有效率n倍<br />\n但通常都係習慣性開電腦睇youtube/掛係到用電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s